'''亨里克·克里斯托弗森'''（{{lang-no|Henrik Kristoffersen}}，{{bd|1994年|7月2日||}}）生于勒伦斯科格，是一名挪威男子高山滑雪运动员<ref>{{cite book|title=Norway Olympic Team and Media Guide Sochi 2014|year=2014|publisher=[[挪威奧林匹克暨殘障奧林匹克委員會和體育同盟|Norwegian Olympic and Paralympic Committee and Confederation of Sports]]|page=25|url=http://www.olympiatoppen.no/om_olympiatoppen/aktuelt/media41483.media|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114023244/http://www.olympiatoppen.no/om_olympiatoppen/aktuelt/media41483.media|archivedate=2021-01-14}}</ref>。他的父亲Lars是一名前滑雪选手，他也在五岁时受父亲的影响开始接触滑雪<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.pyeongchang2018.com/en/game-time/results/OWG2018/en/alpine-skiing/athlete-profile-n3025448-henrik-kristoffersen.htm|title=Athlete Profile: Henrik KRISTOFFERSEN|work=Pyeongchang 2018|accessdate=2021-03-07|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180420010231/https://www.pyeongchang2018.com/en/game-time/results/OWG2018/en/alpine-skiing/athlete-profile-n3025448-henrik-kristoffersen.htm|archivedate=2018-04-20}}</ref>。2012年3月，他完成了个人的世界杯分站赛首秀<ref>{{cite web|url=https://durangoherald.com/articles/260566|title=Henrik Kristoffersen goes winless for a year in slalom|publisher=The Durango Herald|date=2019-01-26|accessdate=2021-03-07|archiveurl=http://web.archive.org/web/20190204134915/https://durangoherald.com/articles/260566|archivedate=2019-02-04}}</ref>。2014年2月，他出战索契冬奥，在曲道项目上以1分42秒67的成绩获得铜牌，以19岁的年龄成为历史上年龄最小的奥运高山滑雪奖牌得主<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2014/02/23/sports/olympics/mario-matt-of-austria-becomes-oldest-olympic-slalom-champion.html|newspaper=New York Times|date=2014-02-22|title=Slalom Champion Sets an Age Record|first=Bill |last=Pennington|accessdate=2021-03-07|archiveurl=http://web.archive.org/web/20200112084743/https://www.nytimes.com/2014/02/23/sports/olympics/mario-matt-of-austria-becomes-oldest-olympic-slalom-champion.html|archivedate=2020-01-12}}</ref>。

